{"tid":1435314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長期吸入催淚彈 可致癌","createTime":"2019-08-09T04:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:12:20.000Z","uid":202720,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7ebd8390a6e2b7d65ad551c9cfd8f0f6c74a5ebd","tid":1435314,"uid":202720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"歐洲議會科學及技術選擇評估報告（European Parliament Science and Technology Options Assessment）詳細研究胡椒噴霧及催淚彈等用於人群控制的化學武器造成的疾病及致命效果，指出兩者能夠造成心臟、肺部及肝臟問題。兩者更可致癌、引致胎兒突變、甚至引致將來的胎兒突變。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.statewatch.org/news/2005/may/steve-wright-stoa-rep.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.statewatch.org%2Fnews%2F2005%2Fmay%2Fsteve-wright-stoa-rep.pdf&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=4a27c596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.statewatch.org/news/2005/may/steve-wright-stoa-rep.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"aff70041992a0e070b5990e10b277a39052fe698","tid":1435314,"uid":108337,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察使用化武攻擊平民</span></span>"},{"pid":"a3381c41525bef0642413eee6db17825bba112c4","tid":1435314,"uid":202720,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"文宣新方向！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港武力組織大規模使用化武！！！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"1eb7000fd20834b6428b4d82534d2932cc57c503","tid":1435314,"uid":72748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"推比其他人知tg 都係化武"},{"pid":"ca61831d937dd3edd7671a402c0b02bc5c341240","tid":1435314,"uid":202720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"b31ff6e96123febe6e7b3ccb2cd9abeff6a2c688","tid":1435314,"uid":202720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:23:26.000Z","m